'''Edward Taylor''' is a first-year medical student who toured the hospital.

==History==
Edward came to the hospital to tour as a medical student. He was assigned to follow [[Jackson Avery]]. They worked on [[Brady Sullivan]], who was trampled by horses on his wedding day. When they took Brady into surgery, he observed. He noticed something on the monitor and tipped the doctors off to a problem, saying they'd just taught his class that.

In his evaluation, he said that Jackson put his own learning opportunities ahead of Edward's.
